text: Bruno Candrian (born 21 May 1947) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
